        Save with our recurring maintenance packages.
      </p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl border border-primary/10">
          <div class="card-body text-center">
            <h3 class="card-title justify-center">Basic</h3>
            <p class="text-base-content/70">Essential lawn care</p>
